3 Steps To Bliss Progression

Sep 19, 2025

View in app

Good morning, dear Family!

This is a very simple progression into feeling the bliss of the dorsal vagal complex. Ashokji always told me to keep pointing myself toward bliss, because it will always guide me in the right direction. What amazing advicebecause by continually orienting toward bliss, you are naturally pointing toward the upper nervous system and the higher mind of the upper chakras.

Blessings and blissings to you and your loved ones!
